list.data:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<RelativeLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    layout_width="fill_parent"
    layout_height="wrap_content"
    click="true"
    orientation="horizontal" >

    <TextView
        id="@+id/fav_item_name"
        layout_width="wrap_content"
        layout_height="42.5dp"
        ellipsize="end"
        function="title"
        gravity="center_vertical"
        paddingLeft="13.5dp"
        singleLine="true"
        textColor="#FF000000"
        textSize="16dp" />

    <LinearLayout
        id="@+id/fav_item_divider"
        layout_width="fill_parent"
        layout_height="1dp"
        layout_alignLeft="@id/fav_item_name"
        layout_alignParentBottom="true"
        background="list_item_divider"
        orientation="horizontal" />

</RelativeLayout>

head.data:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<RelativeLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    layout_width="fill_parent"
    layout_height="44dp"
    background="#FFFAFAFA"
    orientation="vertical" >

    <ImageView
        layout_width="wrap_content"
        layout_height="wrap_content"
        layout_marginLeft="5dp"
        click="back"
        contentDescription="@null"
        scaleType="center"
        src="ic_back" />

    <TextView
        id="@+id/fav_title"
        layout_width="wrap_content"
        layout_height="wrap_content"
        layout_centerInParent="true"
        text="@string/my_fav"
        textColor="#FF000000"
        textSize="20dp" />

    <ImageView
        layout_width="fill_parent"
        layout_height="wrap_content"
        layout_alignParentBottom="true"
        contentDescription="@null"
        scaleType="fitXY"
        src="list_item_divider" />

</RelativeLayout>
